        {
            "id": 6009157,
            "title": "川習通話 習近平：撤銷對中消極舉措 慎重處理台灣問題",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《央視》報導，中國國家主席習近平周四（5 日）晚應約同美國總統川普通話，習近平表示，美方應撤銷對中國實施的消極舉措，慎重處理台灣問題。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009157%2Fl%2F3be84c4318336fef9bae52cb07c3c17e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">中國國家主席習近平周四晚應約同美國總統川普通話。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>習近平指出，根據美方提議，兩國經貿牽頭人在日內瓦舉行會談，邁出通過對話協商解決經貿問題的重要一步，受到兩國各界和國際社會普遍歡迎，也證明對話和合作是唯一正確的選擇。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>習近平說，雙方要用好已經建立的經貿磋商機制，秉持平等態度，尊重各自關切，爭取雙贏結果。對此，中方有誠意，也有原則。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>習近平提到，中國人一向言必行、行必果，既然雙方達成了共識，都應遵守。美中舉行日內瓦會談之後，中方嚴肅認真執行協議。美方應實事求是看待取得的進展，撤銷對中國實施的消極舉措。雙方應增進外交、經貿、軍隊、執法等各領域交流，增進共識、減少誤解、加強合作。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>習近平強調，美國應當慎重處理台灣問題，避免極少數「台獨」分裂分子把中美兩國拖入衝突對抗的危險境地。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《央視》報導，習近平歡迎川普再次訪華，川普表示誠摯感謝。兩國元首同意雙方團隊繼續落實日內瓦共識，儘快舉行新一輪會談。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普說，他十分尊重習近平，美中關係十分重要。美方樂見中國經濟保持強勁成長。美中合作，可以做成很多好事。美方將繼續奉行「一個中國」政策。美方歡迎中國留學生來美學習。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
